query.command:
DEFINE QUERYSET CustomCompanyQuerySet

DEFINE QUERY CompanySummaryQuery ALIAS Companies
SELECT csum.CompanyMd5 WITH IDENTIFIERS, csum.CompanyNameText, csum.BestUrlText, csum.WeKnowCompany, csum.AnchorEmployeeBestKnowerP2PScore, csum.AnchorEmployeePersonMd5, csum.AnchorEmployeeNameText, csum.AnchorJobCompanyName, csum.AnchorTitleText, csum.AnchorIsFormerJob, csum.AnchorEmployeeSeniorityLevel, csum.BestKnowerUserKeyMd5, csum.BestKnowerNameText, csum.WeKnowAnchorEmployeeScore, csum.WeKnowCompanyScore AS Score
FROM CompanySummary csum
WHERE csum.WeKnowCompanyScore >= 0
AND csum.CompanyMd5 IDENTITY @identity
AND csum.CompanyMd5 FIND @find
ORDER BY csum.WeKnowCompanyScore DESC
END QUERY


DEFINE QUERY IntroducerQuery ALIAS Introducers
SELECT ukc.KnoweeCompanyMd5, ukc.ScorePoints AS IntroducerScore, ukc.UserKeyMd5
FROM CompanySummaryQuery main
LINK UserKnowsCompany ukc VIA ukc.KnoweeCompanyMd5 = main.CompanyMd5
ORDER BY ukc.ScorePoints DESC
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE IntroducerDetailQuery ALIAS IntroducerDetail
SELECT psum.PersonMd5 AS IntroducerPersonKeyMd5, psum.PersonNameText AS IntroducerName, psum.BestEmailAddrText AS IntroducerBestEmailAddressText, main.UserKeyMd5 AS IntroducerUserKey
FROM IntroducerQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.MyUserKeyMd5 = main.UserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND GROUPED IntroducerStatsQuery ALIAS IntroducerStats
SELECT ucstat.UserKeyMd5, ucstat.CompanyMd5, ucstat.FirstInboundMsg, ucstat.FirstOutboundMsg, ucstat.FirstMeeting, ucstat.LastInboundMsg, ucstat.LastOutboundMsg, ucstat.LastMeeting
FROM IntroducerQuery main
LINK UserCompanyStat ucstat VIA ucstat.CompanyMd5 = main.KnoweeCompanyMd5
WHERE ucstat.UserKeyMd5 = main.UserKeyMd5
END QUERY


DEFINE QUERY EmployeesQuery ALIAS Employees
SELECT esum.CompanyMd5, esum.PersonNameText, esum.PersonMd5, esum.TitleText, esum.CorpLevelCompanyName, esum.JobCompanyName, esum.SeniorityLevel, esum.IsFormerJob, esum.MyUserKeyMd5, esum.JobCurrentAsOf, esum.WeKnowEmployeeScore AS InfluenceScore, esum.BestKnowerUserKeyMd5 AS KnowerUserKeyMd5, esum.BestKnowerNameText AS KnowerNameText, esum.BestUserKnowsPersonScore AS UserKnowsPersonScore
FROM CompanySummaryQuery main
LINK EmployeeSummary esum VIA esum.CompanyMd5 = main.CompanyMd5
WHERE esum.IsFormerJob != @isCurrentJob
ORDER BY esum.WeKnowEmployeeScore DESC
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE ContactHeadlineQuery ALIAS Contact
SELECT psum.PersonMd5, psum.PersonNameText AS ContactName, psum.BestJobCorpLevelCompanyName AS ContactBestJobCorpLevelCompanyName, psum.BestJobCompanyMd5 AS ContactBestJobCompanyMd5, psum.BestJobMatchedCompanyName AS ContactBestJobMatchedCompanyName, psum.BestJobTitleText AS ContactBestJobTitleText, psum.BestJobIsFormer AS ContactBestJobIsFormer, psum.BestJobCurrentAsOf AS ContactBestJobCurrentAsOf, psum.BestEmailAddrText AS ContactBestEmail, psum.BestEmailCurrentAsOf AS ContactBestEmailAsOf, psum.WeKnowPersonScore
FROM EmployeesQuery pq
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = pq.PersonMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND GROUPED WeInteractWithCompanyQuery ALIAS Stats
SELECT stat.CompanyMd5, stat.FirstInboundMsg, stat.FirstInboundMsgContactMd5, stat.FirstInboundMsgUserKeyMd5, stat.FirstMeeting, stat.FirstMeetingContactMd5, stat.FirstMeetingUserKeyMd5, stat.FirstOutboundMsg, stat.FirstOutboundMsgContactMd5, stat.FirstOutboundMsgUserKeyMd5, stat.LastInboundMsg, stat.LastInboundMsgContactMd5, stat.LastInboundMsgUserKeyMd5, stat.LastMeeting, stat.LastMeetingContactMd5, stat.LastMeetingUserKeyMd5, stat.LastOutboundMsg, stat.LastOutboundMsgContactMd5, stat.LastOutboundMsgUserKeyMd5, stat.NumInboundMsgs, stat.NumMeetings, stat.NumOutboundMsgs
FROM CompanySummaryQuery main
LINK WeInteractWithCompany stat VIA stat.CompanyMd5 = main.CompanyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstInboundMsgUserName ALIAS NameOfFirstInboundMsgUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS FirstInboundMsgUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.FirstInboundMsgUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstOutboundMsgUserName ALIAS NameOfFirstOutboundMsgUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS FirstOutboundMsgUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.FirstOutboundMsgUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstMeetingUserName ALIAS NameOfFirstMeetingUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS FirstMeetingUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.FirstMeetingUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastInboundMsgUserName ALIAS NameOfLastInboundMsgUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS LastInboundMsgUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.LastInboundMsgUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastOutboundMsgUserName ALIAS NameOfLastOutboundMsgUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS LastOutboundMsgUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.LastOutboundMsgUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastMeetingUserName ALIAS NameOfLastMeetingUserName
SELECT usum.ResolvedName AS LastMeetingUserName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK UserSummary usum VIA usum.UserKeyMd5 = main.LastMeetingUserKeyMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstInboundMsgContactName ALIAS NameOfFirstInboundMsgContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS FirstInboundMsgContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.FirstInboundMsgContactMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstOutboundMsgContactName ALIAS NameOfFirstOutboundMsgContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS FirstOutboundMsgContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.FirstOutboundMsgContactMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionFirstMeetingContactName ALIAS NameOfFirstMeetingContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS FirstMeetingContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.FirstMeetingContactMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastInboundMsgContactName ALIAS NameOfLastInboundMsgContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS LastInboundMsgContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.LastInboundMsgContactMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastOutboundMsgContactName ALIAS NameOfLastOutboundMsgContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS LastOutboundMsgContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.LastOutboundMsgContactMd5
END QUERY


EXTEND INLINE InteractionLastMeetingContactName ALIAS NameOfLastMeetingContactName
SELECT psum.PersonNameText AS LastMeetingContactName
FROM WeInteractWithCompanyQuery main
LINK PersonSummary psum VIA psum.PersonMd5 = main.LastMeetingContactMd5
END QUERY


END QUERYSET


EXECUTE QUERYSET CustomCompanyQuerySet
SKIP 0

FOR QUERY CompanySummaryQuery
TAKE 10


FOR QUERY IntroducerQuery
TAKE 100




FOR QUERY EmployeesQuery
TAKE 100
















GO
